title: Journey to the Edge of the Universe (Sean Pertwee - 1080p HD)
description:
A journey through space and time.

After much fruitless time spent in search of a high definition video of the UK version of Journey to the Edge of the Universe featuring narration by Sean Pertwee (and NOT the inferior American version featuring Alec Baldwin),I have edited two videos into one. Audio from a DVD quality UK version dubbed onto the 1080p US version. The US version was made a bit shorter than its UK cousin unfortunately so a bit of narration has had to be culled, however I am happy with the result. I hope you enjoy this documentary as much as I have!
